images.prompt: A majestic steampunk sea queen manifests within an otherworldly abyss, her massive form illuminated by a diffused projector glow that filters through shimmering mist gray and glowing orange hues, her intricate mechanical bones and elaborate armor blending seamlessly into the surreal, bio-mechanical tapestry, her flowing tendrils and intricate tentacles undulating gracefully as a backlit zoom perspective emphasizes the grandeur of her luminous crown and regal presence, casting delicate shadows that dance across her textured surfaces, while her bio-mechanical crown and ornate adornments catch the subtle light, revealing a complex interplay of antiquated gears, porcelain filigree, and glowing phosphor elements, all rendered with hyper-realistic detail in a digital artwork style that immerses viewers into an enigmatic underwater universe where organic elegance meets industrial innovation, creating an ethereal tableau of power, mystery, and celestial beauty, with every tiny rivet, joint, and luminescent filament meticulously crafted to evoke a sense of awe and otherworldly sophistication.
